text:
Holy sh*t.

Via 313 better watch its back, there's a new sheriff in town.

This is the best Detroit style pizza in town.

This pizza is a must try! 

They are not stingy with the toppings and the owner takes pride in what he does and not just looking to make a dollar. 

My kind...
"Go Back To Cali" DOES feel like a personal attack, but in the case of Bat City Pies, I'll accept the gentle insult because it's a damned good slice. It...
